ecom-preorder-g1-page.headingtext_51hygrgupf3_html: Will the leather change or scratch over time?
ecom-preorder-g1-page.textcontent_c94rc2264e_html: Our Horween leather is minimally treated with natural oils and waxes and is therefore prone to scuffing and marking in the first few months of use. With time, scuffs and marks will buff out into a rich and lustrous patina. If you’re looking for a perfect finish, this is not the case for you. If you’re after an authentic leather patina, this is absolutely the case for you.
ecom-preorder-g1-page.headingtext_7esd0ryfzs5_html: What materials are your phone cases made of?
ecom-preorder-g1-page.textcontent_8aitffxn41k_html: Our phone cases are crafted from high-quality materials such as silicone, TPU, hard plastic, and leather. Each material is carefully selected to provide durability, style, and maximum protection for your device.
ecom-preorder-g1-page.headingtext_qi8lks5zyb_html: Can I return or exchange a phone case if it doesn’t fit my device?
ecom-preorder-g1-page.textcontent_nlug2iayb6g_html: Absolutely! If your phone case doesn’t fit, you can return or exchange it within 30 days of purchase. Make sure it’s in its original condition and packaging. Check our return policy for more details.
ecom-preorder-g1-page.headingtext_9ovbfe2pv7i_html: Do you offer customization options for phone cases?
ecom-preorder-g1-page.textcontent_66snffv83d9_html: Yes, we provide customization services for select phone case models. You can add your name, photo, or unique design to make your phone case truly one of a kind. Visit our customization page for more details.
